<p>Sends a sketch of the haricot climbing the shoot of the plum-tree [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">4866</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Hopes to see CD at the [Horticultural] Congress on Wednesday [30 May].</p> 
<p>Sends data on movement direction of <hi rend="italic">Wisteria</hi> shoots.</p> 
